{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    { "src": "api/*.js", "use": "@vercel/node" },
    { "src": "*.html", "use": "@vercel/static" }
  ],
  "routes": [
    { "src": "/api/(.*)", "dest": "/api/$1" },
    { "src": "/(.*\\.html)", "dest": "/$1" }
  ]
}
```

---

## Step 2 — Commit everything

In github.dev click the **Source Control** icon (left sidebar) → type `add vercel config` → click **Commit & Push**

---

## Step 3 — Wait for Vercel to auto-redeploy

Vercel detects the push and rebuilds automatically in ~60 seconds. Watch the **Deployments** tab until it says **Ready**.

